node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，3 月 5 日至 6 月 28 日曾到菲律賓，抵港後由亞洲國際博覽館送院，沒有病徵，與第 #1203 宗個案患者有關連。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health and was in the Philippines between March 5 and June 28. After landing in Hong Kong she was transferred to hospital via the Asia World Expo. She has no symptoms. Her case is epidemiologically linked to the case of patient #1203.
